00:16:01.286 --> 00:16:03.256 A:middle
or else players would
be confused,

00:16:03.256 --> 00:16:04.666 A:middle
and they would become
frustrated,

00:16:04.996 --> 00:16:06.416 A:middle
quit and delete the game.

00:16:06.816 --> 00:16:08.966 A:middle
Wouldn't be a very good
experience for them.

